2280,IssuesEvent,2017-04-02 00:45:53+00:00,18892209,tartley/colorama,1305135,phreakmonkey,,,closed,"autoreset=True doesn't work for file output (Python 3.6.0, Ubuntu)",[],[],2,"I'm not sure if this is a known/expected limitation of autoreset, but it seems to fail to provide the reset codes after each print() in the case of buffer/file output.   

