8018,IssuesEvent,2018-08-29 09:14:02+00:00,1425437,riptano/ccm,3408144,ptnapoleon,275430,riptano,closed,`ccm multitail`,[],[],0,"The other day I saw @nutbunnies using `multitail` to keep an eye on the log for every node in the cluster. It seemed real cool and really useful for debugging. This'd be a good ccm feature, I think. I think I'd also want a `CCM_MULTITAIL_CMD` option so users can use their preferred log-watching tool.
