8097,IssuesEvent,2015-06-15 08:44:11+00:00,374820,celery/billiard,48936,thedrow,319983,celery,opened,Celery Kickstarter,[],[],0,"In order to get this project going we're going to raise funds using Kickstarter.
The work will be performed by @malinoff working on it part time.

**If you'd like to propose yourself as a candidate for funded work please comment here.**

List of tasks we need to do before launching the Kickstarter campain:
- [ ] Define goals.
- [ ] Define stretch goals.
- [ ] Create a video with our proposal.
- [ ] Write the proposal text.
- [ ] Estimate our required budget.
- [ ] Create issues for each goal we agree on.

List of proposed goals as discussed with @malinoff on IRC:
- [ ] Kafka broker support.
- [ ] Using Etcd for discovery of Celery workers instead of using the broker.
- [ ] Using Consul for discovery of Celery workers instead of using the broker.
- [ ] librabbitmq rewrite that will allow it to support Python 3 and PyPy.
- [ ] Bug fixes for critical bugs in Celery that cause Celery to stop consuming tasks.
- [ ] AWS Kinesis broker support.
- [ ] Better support for our experimental brokers.
- [ ] Increasing test coverage, general refactoring, .
- [ ] Automatic autoscaling across the cluster when the task backlog is high or low.
- [ ] An official Docker container for Celery
- [ ] A deployment tool for Celery and the different brokers.

**If you'd like to propose a goal please comment here**",{},{}
