9436,IssuesEvent,2018-08-26 06:01:41+00:00,89379547,zostera/django-bootstrap4,82315,dyve,1092877,zostera,closed,Form layout,[],[],3,"One of the missing things from `django-bootstrap3` was the ability to layout a form. There were a couple of good attempts and PR's to add form layout through classes, but it never clicked. Some people switched to crispy because of the lack of layout. I don't mind people using crispy, but a little help with organizing a form layout would be nice.

