9473,IssuesEvent,2016-07-14 14:50:52+00:00,2665618,inveniosoftware/invenio,5615123,ludmilamarian,1157480,inveniosoftware,closed,WebSearch: UI improvements,"[{'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/labels/c_WebSearch', 'name': 'c_WebSearch', 'color': 'ededed'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/labels/legacy', 'name': 'legacy', 'color': 'd4c5f9'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/labels/p_major', 'name': 'p_major', 'color': 'e11d21'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/labels/t_enhancement', 'name': 't_enhancement', 'color': 'eb6420'}]","[{'login': 'ludmilamarian', 'id': 5615123, 'avatar_url': 'https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/5615123?v=3', 'gravatar_id': '', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/users/ludmilamarian', 'html_url': 'https://github.com/ludmilamarian', 'followers_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/ludmilamarian/followers', 'following_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/ludmilamarian/following{/other_user}', 'gists_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/ludmilamarian/gists{/gist_id}', 'starred_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/ludmilamarian/starred{/owner}{/repo}', 'subscriptions_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/ludmilamarian/subscriptions', 'organizations_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/ludmilamarian/orgs', 'repos_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/ludmilamarian/repos', 'events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/ludmilamarian/events{/privacy}', 'received_events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/ludmilamarian/received_events', 'type': 'User', 'site_admin': False}]",4,"Originally on 2011-04-27

Based on several previous discussions, the search UI could be enriched with:

