10264,IssuesEvent,2018-08-11 09:06:34+00:00,3470471,FortAwesome/Font-Awesome,556268,tagliala,1505683,FortAwesome,closed,Feature request: Remove unwanted icons using an online font builder,[],[],1,"### Describe the problem you'd like to see solved or task you'd like to see made easier

Remove unwanted fonts.

### Is this in relation to an existing part of Font Awesome or something new?

New Feature request.

### What is 1 thing that we can do when building this feature that will guarantee that it is awesome?

A font build tool or some sort which allows me to select fonts that I use and then download it to my personal blog without taking up lot of file size. 11MB is a lot for using 4-6 icons. :)
Examples: fontello.com, icomoon.io

### Why would other Font Awesome users care about this?

1. Bandwidth.
2. Firewall restrictions to use public CDN.
3. App size decreases considerably.

### On a scale of 1 (sometime in the future) to 10 (absolutely right now), how soon would you recommend we make this feature?

I don't want to be selfish and take up lot of your time but sooner the better for the world.

### Feature request checklist

- [ ] This is a single feature (i.e. not a re-write of all of Font Awesome)
- [ ] The title starts with ""Feature request: "" and is followed by a clear feature name (Ex: `Feature request: moar cowbell`)
- [ ] I have [searched for existing issues](https://github.com/FortAwesome/Font-Awesome-Pro/issues) and to the best of my knowledge this is not a duplicate
",{},{}
