10578,IssuesEvent,2018-06-14 14:54:29+00:00,3470471,FortAwesome/Font-Awesome,40008894,bjtb,1505683,FortAwesome,opened,Icon request: icon-object ,[],[],0,"TL;DR: We need an icon for a general object in our app. E.g. circle+square+triangle in one icon, or any other icon that may represent a general, physical object.

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/40008894/41419171-a584fa76-6ff1-11e8-879c-5b1fefe7cddd.png)

Detailed description:
In our app, we have two concepts that are similar: Products and Objects. An object can be anything that may need maintenance or repair (a car, power pole, machinery, etc.) while products are materials/supplies/stock/parts used to repair objects, or other items that may be needed for an assignment and should be charged to the customer. As our app has users from a vast range of industries, both these icons should be quite general. We use a box to represent products, but we need a different and preferably just as general icon for objects.


",{},{}
