11065,IssuesEvent,2016-04-01 17:46:25+00:00,6083592,pympler/pympler,281391,Pankrat,2490143,pympler,closed,pympler segfault when aerospike loaded,[],[],1,"Hi, crossposting this issue https://github.com/aerospike/aerospike-client-python/issues/106 here: 

