11110,IssuesEvent,2015-10-28 17:38:43+00:00,25778634,yhat/db.py,7005192,ppope,2684181,yhat,closed,Query using TRUNCATE fails,[],[],5,"Hi,

Thanks for the very cool implementation. 

When connected to an Amazon Redshift database, my attempt to [TRUNCATE](http://docs.aws.amazon.com/redshift/latest/dg/r_TRUNCATE.html) a table  
```
from db import DB
db = DB() 
db.query(""TRUNCATE table_name;"")
```
