11662,IssuesEvent,2018-08-01 22:14:30+00:00,7209075,pantsbuild/pants,46740,stuhood,3065172,pantsbuild,opened,Add Ctrl+C handling for `--loop`,"[{'id': 268094252, 'node_id': 'MDU6TGFiZWwyNjgwOTQyNTI=', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/pantsbuild/pants/labels/engine', 'name': 'engine', 'color': 'fbca04', 'default': False}]",[],0,"`pantsd` has special handling for `Ctrl+C`, but it does not currently result in breaking out of a `--loop` when executed.

