12775,IssuesEvent,2018-08-03 01:39:19+00:00,50729855,stephenslab/dsc,917985,gaow,5939770,stephenslab,opened,Ignore NA when extracting vector values,[],[],0,"This is related to a side effect of adjustments discussed in #145. Basically when we do not handle `NA` ""smartly"" then in a column like:

