13023,IssuesEvent,2018-04-19 00:42:15+00:00,8566509,delph-in/pydelphin,1428419,goodmami,6363662,delph-in,closed,itsdb key-table mapping is specific to official relations,[],[],1,"Now that there's a project ([XMT](https://github.com/goodmami/xmt)) that uses non-standard relations files for TSDB profiles, it's time to look at assumptions that crept into the code about the database structure. For starters, the `_primary_keys` data structure is not meant to be modified, but it clearly isn't applicable to the alternative DB structure. This affects how a database index is built, which affects row filters, etc.",{},{}
13026,IssuesEvent,2016-03-08 20:20:51+00:00,8566509,delph-in/pydelphin,1428419,goodmami,6363662,delph-in,opened,Variable instantiation problems with DMRS,[],[],0,"There are a couple of issues with variable creation when creating an Xmrs from the `Dmrs()` method:

