usage: az vm image [-h] {show,list-skus,list,list-offers,list-publishers} ...
az vm image: error: the following arguments are required: subcommand
```

well, there are no arguments named `subcommand` as far as I can tell :) Why don't you just say `specify a subcommand` instead?

This message works cmds like the following but not this

```
usage: az storage account create [-h] [--output {json,tsv,list}] [--verbose]
