                                 {Standard_LRS,Standard_GRS,Standard_RAGRS,Standard_ZRS,Premium_LRS}
                                 --name ACCOUNT_NAME [--tags [TAGS]]
                                 --location LOCATION
az storage account create: error: the following arguments are required: --location/-l
```",{},{}
