13474,IssuesEvent,2017-10-26 18:58:44+00:00,51040886,Azure/azure-cli,5723682,tjprescott,6844498,Azure,closed,[DNS] zone import should support @ in RDATA,"[{'id': 418939401, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/Azure/azure-cli/labels/Network', 'name': 'Network', 'color': 'd4c5f9', 'default': False}]","[{'login': 'tjprescott', 'id': 5723682, 'avatar_url': 'https://avatars2.githubusercontent.com/u/5723682?v=4', 'gravatar_id': '', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/users/tjprescott', 'html_url': 'https://github.com/tjprescott', 'followers_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/tjprescott/followers', 'following_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/tjprescott/following{/other_user}', 'gists_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/tjprescott/gists{/gist_id}', 'starred_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/tjprescott/starred{/owner}{/repo}', 'subscriptions_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/tjprescott/subscriptions', 'organizations_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/tjprescott/orgs', 'repos_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/tjprescott/repos', 'events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/tjprescott/events{/privacy}', 'received_events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/tjprescott/received_events', 'type': 'User', 'site_admin': False}]",0,"The following is a legitimate DNS record

www 	3600 	IN	CNAME	@

Currently, this causes a Bad Request error.

This should be imported as a CNAME from www.<$ORIGIN> to <$ORIGIN>.  I.e. where @ is used in RDATA, it should be replaced by $ORIGIN.

Another example might be

w   3600   IN  CNAME   www.@

**Note**: this applies anywhere with a domain name in RDATA. For example, SOA, MX, SRV, PTR, NS, CNAME.  It does not apply to the character '@' when used in a TXT record.

",{},{}
