14262,IssuesEvent,2016-09-05 17:23:33+00:00,28855778,matrix-org/matrix-python-sdk,8479376,gufogio,8418310,matrix-org,opened,client.add_listener does nothing,[],[],0,"Since pull request #32 was merged, `client._sync` does not notify listeners registered on the client, but only those registered on the related room.

I personally find this behavior a little counter-intuitive.

There are two solutions:
 - remove/deprecate `client.add_listener` (to make clear that it won't work)
 - make `client._sync` notify listeners on the client for every event

I would be very happy to submit a pull request after we decide what's better. Thanks :)",{},{}
