14634,IssuesEvent,2016-06-27 16:08:23+00:00,26784827,dotnet/core,14095443,WG-Com,9141961,dotnet,opened,OSX NamedPipeClientStream.get_NumberOfServerInstances() PlatformNotSupportedException,[],[],0,"error:
