File ""/home/ubuntu/anaconda3/envs/job_classification/lib/python3.6/site-packages/cloudpickle/cloudpickle.py"", line 1060, in _make_skel_func
    base_globals['__builtins__'] = __builtins__
TypeError: 'str' object does not support item assignment

How can I fix this issue?",{},{}
