15590,IssuesEvent,2017-08-01 11:11:50+00:00,70238668,CZ-NIC/yangson,10373082,CZNIC-GitLab,11736688,CZ-NIC,closed,Cannot use a submodule's grouping,[],[],0,"Hello,

