*****************
mkhansen@mkhansen-sky1:~/librealsense/build/wrappers/python$ python ~/librealsense/wrappers/python/python-tutorial-1-depth.py 
Traceback (most recent call last):
  File ""/home/mkhansen/librealsense/wrappers/python/python-tutorial-1-depth.py"", line 9, in <module>
    import pyrealsense2 as rs
ImportError: No module named pyrealsense2
mkhansen@mkhansen-sky1:~/librealsense/build/wrappers/python$ ls
CMakeFiles
cmake_install.cmake
Makefile
pybackend2.cpython-35m-x86_64-linux-gnu.so
