pyrealsense2.cpython-35m-x86_64-linux-gnu.so.2.8.1
third_party
***********************
Second, I worked around this by running Python3, but ran into this error:
mkhansen@mkhansen-sky1:~/librealsense/build/wrappers/python$ python3 ~/librealsense/wrappers/python/python-tutorial-1-depth.py 
name 'xrange' is not defined

