16696,IssuesEvent,2017-07-25 17:51:14+00:00,91379993,tensorflow/tensorboard,4317806,wchargin,15658638,tensorflow,closed,Parsing event file spec in Windows,[],[],1,"In `backend.application.parse_event_files_spec` a log directory 'spec' is partitioned with respect to `:` (line 267) to allow the `run_name:path` expression. However, this handicaps Windows user with log directories residing on other drives, e.g. `D:\` as the path is split (without using the `run_name` exp). using `os.path.splitdrive` can solve this, but only if we limit the `run_name` to be longer than 1 letter.",{},{}
