17425,IssuesEvent,2017-06-27 16:39:49+00:00,49804028,jupyterhub/ldapauthenticator,25988196,venkatchetkuri,17927519,jupyterhub,opened,JupyterHub-Livy-Sparkmagic-Kerberos,[],[],0,"Here is my use case:
