- [ ] This is a bug report.
- [ ] This is a feature request.
- [x] This is a plugin (improvement) request.
- [x] I have read the contribution guidelines.

### Description

I was saddened to read after catching up on the latest streamlink issues that a certain plugin has been removed due to a DMCA notice. I do however totally understand and agree with the developers' decision to avoid a major legal headache and comply with the notice.

My query is, would anyone be interested in maintaining the plugin in a separate code repo...?

I'm sure we all know which plugin I refer to, and it was the most life-saving plugin for me ever!

I understand the most recent version is still freely available in the v10 branch, ready to forked and picked up if anyone chose to do so... again, happy to donate to the cause if anyone needs it!",{},{}
