18722,IssuesEvent,2018-07-17 20:22:53+00:00,11309795,nmslib/nmslib,21284577,lkoll,37882366,nmslib,opened,HNSW Parameter Ranges,[],[],0,"Question on parameter ranges that I know you have hinted at in other issues, but as far as I can tell haven't directly addressed. I am also referencing the following link: 

